name: Interactive Screen Saver
description:
This piece is a customazible interactive screensaver. Coded from scratch using p5.js.
Key Map: 
+,- : To speed up/down the rotation
c,x,z    : To randomize color
g,h : To adjust thickness of the lines
r,t : To adjust the size 
k,l : To adjust arc spacing
s:  : To save your settings to the browser storage / Settings are cleared, when browser cache is cleared
